verses.verse: The Lord <WH3068> reigns, <WH4427> He is clothed <WH3847> with majesty; <WH1348> The Lord <WH3068> has clothed <WH3847> and girded <WH247> Himself with strength; <WH5797> Indeed, <WH637> the world <WH8398> is firmly <WH3559> established, <WH3559> it will not be moved. <WH4131>
Thy throne <WH3678> is established <WH3559> from of old; <WH9241> Thou art from everlasting. <WH5769>

The floods <WH5104> have lifted <WH5375> up, O Lord, <WH3068> The floods <WH5104> have lifted <WH5375> up their voice; <WH6963> The floods <WH5104> lift <WH5375> up their pounding <WH1796> waves. <WH1796>

More <WH4480> than <WH4480> the sounds <WH6963> of many <WH7227> waters, <WH4325> [Than] the mighty <WH117> breakers <WH4867> of the sea, <WH3220> The Lord <WH3068> on high <WH4791> is mighty. <WH117>
Thy testimonies <WH9381> are fully <WH3966> confirmed; <WH539> Holiness <WH6944> befits <WH4998> Thy house, <WH1004> O Lord, <WH3068> forevermore. <WH753> <WH3117>
